Imports System Imports System.Data Imports System.Data.Common Imports System.IO Imports System.Collections.Generic Imports System.Globalization Imports System.Linq '20200815-WN-For Stopwatch functions Imports System.Diagnostics
Imports Microsoft.VisualBasic Imports System.Windows.Forms Imports OneStream.Shared.Common Imports OneStream.Shared.Wcf Imports OneStream.Shared.Engine Imports OneStream.Shared.Database Imports OneStream.Stage.Engine Imports OneStream.Stage.Database Imports OneStream.Finance.Engine Imports OneStream.Finance.Database
#Region "Rule Change Mgmt" '-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 'Developer: 20200930-WN-Create inital business rule ' 20201001-WN-Add Start and End Date Columns ' Add Cost Center column ' Add Actity Column - This allows extension to log also other activities ' 20201221-WN-Port Global parameter table function from StoreOps ' Port admin functions from StoreOps ' 20201222-BL-Define parameter data set for BI blend solution ' 20210302-WN-Add XFT_CFR_Dashboard_POV_Matrix table ' 20210330-WN-Add Expense Planning Test table ' 20210426-KN-Add XFT_OrphanedDT '-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- #End Region
Namespace OneStream.BusinessRule.DashboardExtender.ENS_CustomTables_SolutionHelper Public Class MainClass
#Region "Main" Public Function Main(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardExtenderArgs) As Object Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Try Select Case args.FunctionType Case Is = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.ComponentSelectionChanged Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As XFSelectionChangedTaskResult = Nothing
If (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("createCustomTable")) Then Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("tableName") selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.createCustomTable(si, tableName, "single") Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("createPackageCustomTables")) Then Dim packageName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("packageName") selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.createPackageCustomTables(si, packageName) If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "After createPackageCustomTables call for package " & packageName) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("inspectCustomTable")) Then Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("tableName") selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.inspectCustomTable(si, tableName) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf(args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("updateCustomTable")) Then Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("tableName") selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.updateCustomTable(si, tableName) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("clearCustomTable")) Then '20200630-WN-Not yet implemented Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("tableName") Dim upToDate As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("upToDate") selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.clearCustomTable(si, tableName, upToDate) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("dropCustomTable")) Then Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("tableName") selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.dropCustomTable(si, tableName) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ImportCSVFile")) Then selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.ImportCSVFileMain(si, globals, api, args) If Not Me.m_CustomEvents Is Nothing Then Me.m_CustomEvents.AfterSelectionChangedEvent(si, globals, api, args, selectionChangedTaskResult) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ImportXLSXFile")) Then 'Upload XFT formatted spreadsheets selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.ImportXLSXFileMain(si, globals, api, args) If Not Me.m_CustomEvents Is Nothing Then Me.m_CustomEvents.AfterSelectionChangedEvent(si, globals, api, args, selectionChangedTaskResult) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
ElseIf (args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("ExportToCSV")) Then selectionChangedTaskResult = Me.ExportToCSV(si, globals, api, args) If Not Me.m_CustomEvents Is Nothing Then Me.m_CustomEvents.AfterSelectionChangedEvent(si, globals, api, args, selectionChangedTaskResult) Return selectionChangedTaskResult
End If
Case Is = DashboardExtenderFunctionType.SqlTableEditorSaveData 'SQL Table Editor functions If args.FunctionName.XFEqualsIgnoreCase("updateAuditInfo") Then 'Update audit columns timestap and update user 'Validate columns with constraints Return Me.updateAuditInfo(si, args) End If
End Select
Return Nothing Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function #End Region
#Region "Create individual custom tables" Public Function createCustomTable(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal tableName As String, ByVal processMode As String) 'Prepare SQL Dim sql As New Text.StringBuilder Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("Business Rule: createCustomTable. Mode: " & processMode) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "processMode " & processMode & " for " & tableName)
Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) 'Check if table exists already before running SQL If (DBSql.DoesTableExist(dbConnApp, tableName)) selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True statusReport.AppendLine("Custom table " & tableName & " exists already.") selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Custom table " & tableName & " exists already.") If processMode = "single" Then Return selectionChangedTaskResult Else Return statusReport End If End If
Select Case tableName 'Custom Tables for ENS Case Is = "XFT_ExpensePlanning_Test" '2021-MAR-30 WN I just used arbitrary length for columns beyond cost center sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_ExpensePlanning_Test] ") sql.AppendLine("( ")
sql.AppendLine(" [CostCenter] [varchar] (7), ") sql.AppendLine(" [GLAccount] [varchar] (10), ") sql.AppendLine(" [LineItem] [varchar] (4), ") sql.AppendLine(" [LineItemDescription] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [ServiceType] [varchar] (200), ")
sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20) ")
sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([CostCenter], [GLAccount], [LineItem] ) ") sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_FCST_Store_Map" sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_FCST_Store_Map] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Store_Source] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Store_Target] [varchar] (200), ")
sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20) ")
sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([Store_Source]) ") sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_FCST_GL_Map" sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_FCST_GL_Map] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module] [varchar] (10), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module_Desc] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Select_Module] [bit] , ") sql.AppendLine(" [Sub_Module] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Sub_Module_Desc] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Select_Sub_Module] [bit] , ") sql.AppendLine(" [GL] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [GL_Desc] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Select_GL] [bit] , ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20), ") sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([GL]) ") sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_FCST_Module_Map" sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_FCST_Module_Map] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module] [varchar] (10), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module_Desc] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Select_Module] [bit] , ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20), ") sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([Module]) ") sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_FCST_Module_View" sql.AppendLine("CREATE VIEW [dbo].[XFT_FCST_Module_View] AS") sql.AppendLine(" Select a.Module, a.Module_Desc,a.Select_Module, b.Sub_Module, b.Sub_Module_Desc, b.Select_Sub_Module, c.GL, c.GL_Desc,c.Select_GL ") 'sql.AppendLine(" Select XFT_FCST_Module_Map.Module, XFT_FCST_Module_Map.Module_Desc,XFT_FCST_Module_Map.Select_Module, XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map.Sub_Module, XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map.Sub_Module_Desc, XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map.Select_Sub_Module ") 'sql.AppendLine(" From XFT_FCST_Module_Map Inner Join XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map ON XFT_FCST_Module_Map .Module=XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map.Module") sql.AppendLine(" From XFT_FCST_Module_Map As a Inner Join XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map As b ON a.Module=b.Module Inner Join XFT_FCST_Account_Map As c On b.Module = c.Module ") sql.AppendLine(" Where a.Select_Module = 1 OR b.Select_Sub_Module = 1 OR c.Select_GL = 1")
Case Is = "XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map" sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_FCST_Sub_Module_Map] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Sub_Module] [varchar] (10), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Sub_Module_Desc] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Select_Sub_Module] [bit] , ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module] [varchar] (10), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20), ") sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([Sub_Module]) ") sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_FCST_Account_Map" sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_FCST_Account_Map] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [GL] [varchar] (20), ") sql.AppendLine(" [GL_Desc] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Select_GL] [bit] , ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module] [varchar] (10), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20), ") sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([GL]) ") sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_CFR_Dashboard_POV_Matrix" '20210302-WN-Table used to store possible POVs for Fcst Cube View output to data tables sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_CFR_Dashboard_POV_Matrix] ") sql.AppendLine("( ")
sql.AppendLine(" [CategoryCFR] [varchar] (200) NOT NULL, ") sql.AppendLine(" [PovId] [varchar] (30) NOT NULL, ")
sql.AppendLine(" [Scenario_TY] [varchar] (50) NOT NULL, ") sql.AppendLine(" [Scenario_EFC] [varchar] (50) NOT NULL, ") sql.AppendLine(" [Time] [varchar] (30) NOT NULL, ") sql.AppendLine(" [Entity] [varchar] (200) NOT NULL, ") sql.AppendLine(" [CenterType] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [ChannelLevel] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [eCommLevel] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [AudityTrail] [varchar] (200), ")
sql.AppendLine(" [AdapterName] [varchar] (200) NOT NULL, ")
sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20) ")
sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([CategoryCFR], [PovId]) ")
sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog" '20200930-WN-Added table sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Segment] [varchar] (30) NOT NULL, ") sql.AppendLine(" [Activity] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [SubmWeek] [varchar] (30), ") sql.AppendLine(" [CostCenter] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [SubmTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, " ) sql.AppendLine(" [UserName] [varchar] (50) DEFAULT SYSTEM_USER, " ) sql.AppendLine(" [UserDesc] [varchar] (200) ") sql.AppendLine(" )") Case Is = "XFT_Global_Parameters" '2020121-WN-Ported from storeOps ' Add New table To store environment specific parameters sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_Global_Parameters] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Module] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [AppName] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [ParmName] [varchar] (200), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Action] [varchar] (20), ") sql.AppendLine(" [SeqNum] [int] DEFAULT 0, ") sql.AppendLine(" [ParmValue] [nvarchar] (max), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Description] [nvarchar] (200), ")
sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20) ")
sql.AppendLine(" PRIMARY KEY ([Module],[AppName],[ParmName],[Action],[SeqNum]) ")
sql.AppendLine(")") Case Is = "XFT_BI_Blend_Cost_Center_Group" '20201207-BL-Define parameter data set for BI blend solution table 1 sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_BI_Blend_Cost_Center_Group] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Load_Process] [nvarchar] (40) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', ") sql.AppendLine(" [Cost_Center_Group] [nvarchar] (40) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', ") sql.AppendLine(" [Cost_Center] [nvarchar] (7) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', ")
sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20) ") sql.AppendLine(" )") Case Is = "XFT_BI_Blend_Fiscal_Period" '20201207-BL-Define parameter data set for BI blend solution table 2 sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_BI_Blend_Fiscal_Period] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [Load_Process] [nvarchar] (40) NOT NULL DEFAULT '', ") sql.AppendLine(" [Fiscal_Period_Key] INT, ")
sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateTime] [datetime] DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, ") sql.AppendLine(" [UpdateBy][varchar] (20) ") sql.AppendLine(" )") '20210426-KN- Creates New Orphaned Data Table Case Is = "XFT_OrphanedDT" sql.AppendLine("CREATE TABLE [dbo].[XFT_OrphanedDT] ") sql.AppendLine("( ") sql.AppendLine(" [RowID] [varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Cube] [varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Entity] [varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Scenario][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Time][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Consolidation][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Origin][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [IC][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Flow][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [Account][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD1][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD2][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD3][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD4][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD5][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD6][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD7][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine(" [UD8][varchar] (40), ") sql.AppendLine("[Amount][varchar] (50),") sql.AppendLine(" )") End Select Try If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "SQL:" & sql.ToString()) 'Execute Query on App DB BRApi.Database.ExecuteActionQuery (dbConnApp, sql.ToString, False, False) statusReport.AppendLine("Created custom table " & tableName & ".") Catch ex As Exception selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("Could Not create custom table " & tableName & ".") statusReport.AppendLine("Error " & ex.Message & ".") BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Cannot create custom table " & tableName & ". Error:" & ex.Message & ".") End Try End Using selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString If processMode = "single" Then Return selectionChangedTaskResult Else Return statusReport End If End Function #End Region
#Region "Create custom tables by package" Private Function createPackageCustomTables(ByRef si As SessionInfo, ByVal packageName As String) '20201221-WN-Dashboard passes package name Global ' Function calls individual custom table create functions Dim tableNames(2) As String Dim i As Integer = 0 Dim createTables As Boolean = False Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder Dim tableResult As New Text.StringBuilder Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True
statusReport.AppendLine("Business Rule: createPackageCustomTables for package " & packageName) If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "createPackageCustomTables for package " & packageName) Select Case packageName Case Is = "Global" ReDim Preserve tableNames(2) tableNames = {"XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog", "XFT_Global_Parameters"} createTables = True Case Else If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Unmanaged package " & packageName) End Select If createTables Then If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Create tables for package " & packageName) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "uBound tables " & uBound(tableNames).ToString) End If For Each tableName As String In tableNames If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Calling createCustomTable for " & tableName) tableResult = Me.createCustomTable(si, tableName, "package") statusReport.AppendLine(tableResult.ToString) Next If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Completed looping over all tables to be created for package " & packageName) Else If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "No tables to be created for package " & packageName) End If If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Before sending results back to calling function")
Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() If selectionChangedTaskResult IsNot Nothing Then selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = True selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult Else If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "selectionChangedTaskResult is not an object") Return Nothing End If End Function #End Region
#Region "Inspect Custom Table Function" Private Function inspectCustomTable(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal tableName As String) Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim sql As New Text.StringBuilder Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("Dashboard Extender BR:ENS_CustomTables_SolutionHelper - Function: inspectCustomTable.") statusReport.AppendLine("This function is used to evaluate columns in custom tables to determine if table requires updates.") statusReport.AppendLine("")
Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) Try sql.AppendLine("SELECT TABLE_NAME, COLUMN_NAME, DATA_TYPE, ") sql.AppendLine("CASE ") sql.AppendLine(" WHEN DATA_TYPE = 'NUMERIC' OR DATA_TYPE = 'DECIMAL' THEN ") sql.AppendLine(" TRIM(CAST(NUMERIC_PRECISION AS CHAR)) + ',' + CAST(NUMERIC_SCALE AS CHAR)") sql.AppendLine(" ELSE ") sql.AppendLine(" CAST(CHARACTER_MAXIMUM_LENGTH AS CHAR) ") sql.AppendLine("END [COLSIZE]") sql.AppendLine("FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS ") sql.AppendLine("WHERE TABLE_NAME = '" & tableName & "'")
If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("SQL Statement") statusReport.AppendLine(sql.ToString) End If Dim firstRow As Boolean = True Using dt As DataTable = BRAPi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConnApp, sql.ToString, True) If Not dt.Rows.Count = 0 Then For Each dataRow As DataRow In dt.Rows Dim dr_tableName As String = trim(dataRow.Field(Of String)("TABLE_NAME")) Dim dr_columnName As String = trim(dataRow.Field(Of String)("COLUMN_NAME")) Dim dr_dataType As String = trim(dataRow.Field(Of String)("DATA_TYPE")) Dim dr_colSize As String = trim(dataRow.Field(Of String)("COLSIZE") ) Dim colScale As Integer = 0 Dim colPrecision As Integer = 0
If firstRow Then statusReport.AppendLine("tableName: " & dr_tableName) statusReport.AppendLine("") firstRow = False End If statusReport.AppendLine("Column: " & dr_columnName) statusReport.AppendLine("DataType: " & dr_dataType & " size: " & dr_colSize)
Select Case dr_columnName Case Is = "numeric" statusReport.AppendLine("Numeric column. Size: " & dr_colSize) Case Is = "decimal" 'Parse precision and scale Dim decColDef As String() = dr_colSize.Split(",") statusReport.AppendLine("Decimal column. decColDef(0) Precision: " & decColDef(0) & " decColDef(1) # decimals: " & decColDef(1)) Case Is = "varchar" statusReport.AppendLine("Text column. Size: " & dr_colSize) Case Is = "int", "smallint" statusReport.AppendLine("Int column.") Case Is = "date" statusReport.AppendLine("date column.") End Select
Select Case dr_tableName 'Table inspection to evaluate if change is required Case Is = "Sample" Select Case dr_columnName Case Is = "Sample" If dr_colSize.ToString = "5,4" Then statusReport.AppendLine("dr_columnName " & dr_columnName & " check passed.") Else statusReport.AppendLine("Need to alter " & dr_columnName & " to Decimal 5,4.") End If Case Else End Select End Select statusReport.AppendLine("") Next Else If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("dt.Rows.Count: " & dt.Rows.Count.ToString) End If End Using
Catch ex As Exception selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("No result set returned by sql statement. Exception " & ex.Message) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "No result set returned by sql statement. Exception " & ex.Message) End Try End Using
selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End Function #End Region
#Region "Custom table maintenance functions" Private Function updateCustomTable(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal tableName As String) '20200630-WN-Add new sub routine to alter tables once app is in QA. ' This sub routine will be built out to eventually work of a text file in the dashboard Dim sql As New Text.StringBuilder Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim runSQL As Boolean = False Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("Business Rule: updateCustomTable")
Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) 'Test if table exists already. If not end function. User has to use different dashboard function. If (Not DBSql.DoesTableExist(dbConnApp, tableName)) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Custom table " & tableName & " not yet created.") selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True statusReport.AppendLine("Custom table " & tableName & " not yet created.") selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End If
Select Case tableName Case Is = "XFT_ExpensePlanning_Test" '2021-MAR-30 WN Prepare section for columns to be updated
Case Is = "XFT_CFR_Dashboard_POV_Matrix" Dim addEcommLevel As Boolean = (Not DBSql.DoesColumnExist(dbConnApp, tableName, "eCommLevel")) If addEcommLevel Then sql.AppendLine("") sql.AppendLine("ALTER TABLE [dbo].[XFT_CFR_Dashboard_POV_Matrix] ") sql.AppendLine("ADD [eCommLevel] [varchar] (200) ") runSQL = True End If Case Is = "XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog" Dim addUserDesc As Boolean = (Not DBSql.DoesColumnExist(dbConnApp, tableName, "UserDesc")) If addUserDesc Then sql.AppendLine("") sql.AppendLine("ALTER TABLE [dbo].[XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog] ") sql.AppendLine("ADD [UserDesc] [varchar] (200) ") runSQL = True End If End Select
If runSQL Then Try 'Execute Query on App DB BRApi.Database.ExecuteActionQuery (dbConnApp, sql.ToString, False, False) statusReport.AppendLine("Updated custom table " & tableName) Catch ex As Exception selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("SQL Statement failed. " & sql.ToString) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Cannot update custom table " & tableName & " Error:" & ex.Message.ToString()) End Try Else statusReport.AppendLine("No updates for " & tableName) End If End Using
selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End Function
Private Function clearCustomTable(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal tableName As String, ByVal upToDate As String) Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim sql As New Text.StringBuilder Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("Business Rule: clearCustomTable for " & tableName & " clear up to " & upToDate)
If tableName = "XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog" Then 'check if date is valid Dim isValidDate As Boolean = IsDate(upToDate) If Not isValidDate Then statusReport.AppendLine("Enter a valid date to clear " & tableName) selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End If End If
Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) If (Not DBSql.DoesTableExist(dbConnApp, tableName)) selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True statusReport.AppendLine("Custom table " & tableName & " does not exist.") selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString If DEBUG Then BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Custom table " & tableName & " does not exist.") Return selectionChangedTaskResult End If
sql.AppendLine("DELETE From [dbo].[" & tableName & "]")
If tableName = "XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog" Then sql.AppendLine("WHERE [SubmTime] < '" & upToDate & "'") End If If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("Clear SQL " & sql.ToString) Try BRApi.Database.ExecuteActionQuery (dbConnApp, sql.ToString, False, False) If tableName = "XFT_ENS_Activity_AuditLog" Then statusReport.AppendLine("Table " & tableName & " cleared up to " & upToDate & ".") Else statusReport.AppendLine("Table " & tableName & " cleared.") End If Catch ex As Exception selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("Could Not run SQL " & sql.ToString) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Could Not run SQL " & sql.ToString) End Try End Using
selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End Function
Private Function dropCustomTable(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal tableName As String) '20200630-WN-Add new sub routine to alter tables once app is in QA. ' This sub routine will be built out to eventually work of a text file in the dashboard Dim sql As New Text.StringBuilder Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("Business Rule: dropCustomTable")
Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) Try 'Execute Query on App DB 'Table must exist already before running SQL If (Not DBSql.DoesTableExist(dbConnApp, tableName)) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Custom table " & tableName & " not yet created.") selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("Custom table " & tableName & " not yet created.") Else 'sql.AppendLine("DROP VIEW " & tableName) sql.AppendLine("DROP TABLE " & tableName) Using dt As DataTable = BRAPi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConnApp, sql.ToString, True) If Not dt Is Nothing Then 'Reference dt to access data table results dt.TableName = "SQLResult" selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = True statusReport.AppendLine("Table " & tableName & " has been dropped.") Else BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "No dt object returned after ExecuteSQL") selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("No result set returned by sql statement " & sql.ToString) End If End Using End If Catch ex As Exception selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("No result set returned by sql statement " & sql.ToString) BRAPi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Cannot drop custom table " & tableName & ". SQL:" & sql.ToString()) End Try End Using selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End Function #End Region
#Region "Validate Data Submission" Private Function updateAuditInfo(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal args As DashboardExtenderArgs) As XFSqlTableEditorSaveDataTaskResult Try Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim ValidationFail As Boolean = False Dim updateAuditCols As Boolean = False Dim saveDataTaskResult As New XFSqlTableEditorSaveDataTaskResult() 'Initialize task results saveDataTaskResult.IsOK = True saveDataTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = False Dim localNow As DateTime = DateTime.Now Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("tableName") Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("Function: updateAuditInfo for " & tableName)
'Loop over edited/new rows Dim saveDataTaskInfo As XFSqlTableEditorSaveDataTaskInfo = args.SqlTableEditorSaveDataTaskInfo For Each xfRow As XFEditedDataRow In saveDataTaskInfo.EditedDataRows If (xfRow.InsertUpdateOrDelete = DbInsUpdateDelType.Update) Or (xfRow.InsertUpdateOrDelete = DbInsUpdateDelType.Insert) Then Select Case tableName Case Is = "XFT_ExpensePlanning_Test" 'Add validation code. Samples can be found in StoreOps version of this business rule updateAuditCols = True Case Is = "XFT_FCST_GL_Map"
updateAuditCols = True Case Is = "XFT_FCST_Store_Map"

If ValidationFail Then saveDataTaskResult.IsOK = False saveDataTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True End If saveDataTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString saveDataTaskResult.CancelDefaultSave = False 'Note: Use True if we already saved the data rows in this Business Rule. Return saveDataTaskResult

#Region "Export To simple CSV format" Public Function ExportToCSV(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardExtenderArgs) As XFSelectionChangedTaskResult Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("Table") Dim fileName As String = tableName & ".csv" Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder Dim sql As New Text.StringBuilder Dim columnName As String Dim firstRow As Boolean = True Dim fieldList As New List(Of String) Dim fieldListParam As String = ""
statusReport.AppendLine("Business Rule: ExportToCSV - Create CSV File") If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("Button Parm: tableName:" & tableName)
'20201130-WN-Derive columns with SQL to build fieldList rather than requiring parameter Using dbConnApp As DBConnInfo = BRApi.Database.CreateApplicationDbConnInfo(si) Try sql.AppendLine("SELECT COLUMN_NAME ") sql.AppendLine("FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS ") sql.AppendLine("WHERE TABLE_NAME = '" & tableName & "'")
Using dt As DataTable = BRAPi.Database.ExecuteSql(dbConnApp, sql.ToString, True) If Not dt.Rows.Count = 0 Then For Each dr As DataRow In dt.Rows columnName = dr.Field(Of String)("COLUMN_NAME") '20201202-WN-Do not export audit columns Select Case columnName Case "UpdateTime", "UpdateBy" 'skip If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("Column " & columnName & " skipped.") Case Else fieldList.Add(columnName) If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("Column " & columnName & " added to field list.") End Select If firstRow Then firstRow = False Next fieldListParam = String.Join(";", fieldList.ToArray()) 'for header row End If End Using If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("fieldList:" & fieldList.ToString) statusReport.AppendLine("fieldListParam:" & fieldListParam) End If Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) statusReport.AppendLine("Exception:" & ex.Message) Return Nothing End Try End Using
Try 'Export the records of table to CSV file Dim getCustomTableExpression As String = fieldList(0).ToString & " Like '%'" Dim dt As DataTable = BRApi.Database.GetCustomDataTable(si, "Application", tableName, getCustomTableExpression) If dt Is Nothing Then If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("No DataTable") Else Try If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("Row count in data table:" & dt.Rows.Count) If dt.Rows.Count <> 0 Then Dim delimiter As String = ";"
Dim sSubFolder As String = "\Groups\Everyone\" Dim AdminRespFolderPath As String = BRAPi.Utilities.GetFileShareFolder(si, FileShareFolderTypes.ApplicationIncoming, Nothing).Replace("\Incoming","") & sSubFolder Dim sTargetFileSW As StreamWriter = New StreamWriter(AdminRespFolderPath & fileName) statusReport.AppendLine("CSV file is stored at " & AdminRespFolderPath & fileName & ". Click OK to continue.")
'Add field header to output 'sTargetFileSW.WriteLine(fieldListParam.Replace(";", delimiter)) sTargetFileSW.WriteLine(fieldListParam) For Each oRow As DataRow In dt.Rows Dim fieldCounter As Integer = 1 For Each sField As String In fieldList sTargetFileSW.Write(oRow(sField)) If fieldCounter < fieldList.Count Then sTargetFileSW.Write(delimiter) fieldCounter = fieldCounter + 1 Else sTargetFileSW.WriteLine("") End If Next Next oRow
sTargetFileSW.Close Else If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("No rows returned in data table") End If selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = True Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("Exception:" & ex.Message) End Try End If Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = False statusReport.AppendLine("GetCustomDataTable Exception:" & ex.Message) End Try
selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString Return selectionChangedTaskResult End Function #End Region
#Region "Import simple CSV format" Public Function ImportCSVFileMain(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardExtenderArgs) As XFSelectionChangedTaskResult 'LoadCustomTableUsingelimitedFileMethod '20201107-WN-Add function to allow loading of csv file to custom table. ' This will enable to extract to CSV from one environment and load to another environment Try Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True If DEBUG Then BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Begin ImportCSVFileMain ") Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim filePath As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FilePath") Dim tableName As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("TableName")
Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("WMTOps_CustomTables_SolutionHelper - Function: Load Custom Table ImportCSVFileMain. ") If DEBUG Then statusReport.AppendLine("Function ImportCSVFileMain") statusReport.AppendLine("Parm: filePath " & filePath) statusReport.AppendLine("Parm: tableName " & tableName) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "filePath " & filePath & " tableName " & tableName) End If
'Process the uploaded file Dim loadResults As List(Of TableRangeContent) = Me.ImportCSVFile(si, filePath, tableName) statusReport.AppendLine(StringHelper.FormatMessage(Me.m_MsgFileLoaded, filePath))
selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = True selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True Return selectionChangedTaskResult Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function
Private Function ImportCSVFile(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal filePath As String, ByVal tableName As String) As List(Of TableRangeContent) Try Dim DEBUG As Boolean = True If DEBUG Then BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Function: ImportCSVFile, filePath parm " & filePath &", tableName parm " & tableName)
Dim delimitedFileNameOrFileSharePath As String = filePath Dim delimiter As String = ";" Dim dbLocation As String = "Application" Dim loadMethod As String = "Merge" Dim skipHeaderRow As Boolean = True 'For each table we need a list of fieldTokens. These are the tokens that are in the XFT spreadshet
Dim fieldTokens As New List(Of String) Select Case tableName Case Is = "XFT_Global_Parameters" 'Module;ParmName;AppName;ParmValue fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[Module]") fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[AppName]") fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[ParmName]") fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[Action]") fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[SeqNum]") fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[ParmValue]") fieldTokens.Add("xfText#:[Description]") Case Else If DEBUG Then BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "Unmanaged table " & tableName & ". Cannot run ImportCSVFile.") Return Nothing End Select
'Get the upload "TEMP" file from the database file system Dim fileInfo As XFFileEx = BRApi.FileSystem.GetFile(si, FileSystemLocation.ApplicationDatabase, filePath, True, False, False, SharedConstants.Unknown, Nothing, True) If DEBUG Then BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "fileInfo " & fileInfo.ToString) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "fileInfo.XFFile.FileInfo.FolderFullName " & fileInfo.XFFile.FileInfo.FolderFullName) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "fileInfo.XFFile.FileInfo.FileSystemLocation " & fileInfo.XFFile.FileInfo.FileSystemLocation) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "fileInfo.XFFile.FileInfo " & fileInfo.XFFile.FileInfo.ToString) End If
Dim loadResults As TableRangeContent = BRApi.Utilities.LoadCustomTableUsingDelimitedFile(si, SourceDataOriginTypes.FromFileUpload, filePath, fileInfo.XFFile.ContentFileBytes, delimiter, dbLocation, tableName, loadMethod, fieldTokens, skipHeaderRow)
If DEBUG Then BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults FieldTokens " & loadResults.FieldTokens.ToString) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults GetErrorMessage " & loadResults.GetErrorMessage.ToString) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults HasInvalidDataRows " & loadResults.HasInvalidDataRows) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults HasInvalidFieldNames " & loadResults.HasInvalidFieldNames) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults InvalidDataRows " & loadResults.InvalidDataRows.ToString) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults InvalidFieldNames" & loadResults.InvalidFieldNames.ToString) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults LoadMethod " & loadResults.LoadMethod) BRAPI.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si, "loadResults TableName " & loadResults.TableName) End If
' 'Delete the temp file ' BRApi.FileSystem.DeleteFile(si, FileSystemLocation.ApplicationDatabase, filePath) Return Nothing 'loadResults
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) Finally Try 'Delete the temp file BRApi.FileSystem.DeleteFile(si, FileSystemLocation.ApplicationDatabase, filePath) Catch End Try End Try End Function
#End Region
#Region "Constants And Enumerations" 'String Constants Public m_FileExtension As String = "xlsx" Public m_SameProfile As String = "(SameProfile)" 'Custom Event Handler Declaration Dim m_CustomEvents As Object = Nothing 'String Messages Private m_MsgXLSXRequired As String = "Error: Import file must be Of type XLSX." Private m_MsgFileLoaded As String = "File [{0}] Loaded" Private m_MsgFileNotLoaded As String = "File could Not be loaded, workflows have been completed based On existing register/activity data." #End Region
#Region "Import XLSX File" Public Function ImportXLSXFileMain(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal globals As BRGlobals, ByVal api As Object, ByVal args As DashboardExtenderArgs) As XFSelectionChangedTaskResult Try Dim DEBUG As Boolean = False Dim selectionChangedTaskResult As New XFSelectionChangedTaskResult() Dim filePath As String = args.NameValuePairs.XFGetValue("FilePath") If DEBUG Then BRApi.ErrorLog.LogMessage(si,"filePath " & filePath)
Dim statusReport As New Text.StringBuilder statusReport.AppendLine("WMTOps_CustomTables_SolutionHelper - Function: Load XFT Custom Table Template. ")
'Process the uploaded file Dim loadResults As List(Of TableRangeContent) = Me.ImportXLSXFile(si, filePath) statusReport.AppendLine(StringHelper.FormatMessage(Me.m_MsgFileLoaded, filePath))
'20201021-WN-Evaluate load result. For Each XFT_Range As TableRangeContent In loadResults statusReport.AppendLine("Table: " & XFT_Range.TableName & " loaded With Load Method: " & XFT_Range.LoadMethod & ". ")
Select Case XFT_Range.TableName Case Is = "XFT_SupplyCosts_Parameters" statusReport.AppendLine("Validating table " & XFT_Range.TableName & ".")
Case Is = "XFT_StoreInfo" statusReport.AppendLine("Validating table " & XFT_Range.TableName & ".") Case Is = "XFT_Global_Parameters" statusReport.AppendLine("Validating table " & XFT_Range.TableName & ".") Case Else statusReport.AppendLine("Unmonitored custom table. ") End Select Next selectionChangedTaskResult.Message = statusReport.ToString
'Show a message box that the file was processed selectionChangedTaskResult.IsOK = True selectionChangedTaskResult.ShowMessageBox = True Return selectionChangedTaskResult
Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) End Try End Function
Private Function ImportXLSXFile(ByVal si As SessionInfo, ByVal filePath As String) As List(Of TableRangeContent) Try Dim loadResults As New List(Of TableRangeContent) 'Validate the file type If Not filePath.XFContainsIgnoreCase(Me.m_FileExtension) Then Throw New XFUserMsgException(si, Nothing, Nothing, m_MsgXLSXRequired) End If
'Get the upload "TEMP" file from the database file system Dim fileInfo As XFFileEx = BRApi.FileSystem.GetFile(si, FileSystemLocation.ApplicationDatabase, filePath, True, False, False, SharedConstants.Unknown, Nothing, True)
'Load Excel File 'Note: dbLocation, TableName, LoadMethod & Field names defined in header of each excel "xft" range. loadResults = BRApi.Utilities.LoadCustomTableUsingExcel(si, SourceDataOriginTypes.FromFileUpload, "Temp.xlsx", fileInfo.XFFile.ContentFileBytes)
'Delete the temp file BRApi.FileSystem.DeleteFile(si, FileSystemLocation.ApplicationDatabase, filePath) Return loadResults Catch ex As Exception Throw ErrorHandler.LogWrite(si, New XFException(si, ex)) Finally Try 'Delete the temp file BRApi.FileSystem.DeleteFile(si, FileSystemLocation.ApplicationDatabase, filePath) Catch End Try End Try End Function #End Region
End Class End Namespace
